acceptOwnership().details: New owner pending to accept ownership executes this function to confirm his ownership.

allowBlacklistedUserAddress(address).details: Allow user address back to normal, only admin can do it.

approveKYCUserAddress(address).details: Approve KYC user address, only admin can do it.

blacklistUserAddress(address).details: Blacklist user address, only admin can do it.

disapproveKYCUserAddress(address).details: Disapprove KYC user address, only admin can do it.

enableDeposits(bool).details: Enable deposits if they are disabled, executed only by admin.

params.enable: True to enable, false to disable.

enableTransfers(bool).details: Enable transfers if they are disabled, executed only by admin.

enableWithdrawals(bool).details: Enable withdrawals if they are disabled, executed only by admin.

isBlacklisted(address).details: Check if user address is blacklisted.

isKYCApproved(address).details: Check if user address is KYC approved.

kill().details: Destroy contract eliminating it from the blockchain

reclaimEther(address).details: Send all eth balance in the contract to another address

params._to: Address to send contract ether balance to

setFeesCollectorWallet(address).details: Change transfer fees collector wallet, only owner can do it

params.newWallet: Set address to collect fees into

setMaxWithdrawalAmount(uint256).details: Set/change maximum withdrawal amount, only admin can do it.

setMinWithdrawalAmount(uint256).details: Set/change minimum withdrawal amount, only admin can do it.

setName(bytes32).details: Change contract name, only admin can do it.

setTransferToYourselfIsWidrawal(bool).details: Set transfer to yourself is widrawal toggle enabled/disabled.

params._newOwner: New owner address acquiring ownership of contract
